headline.main: Russia's Will to Fight; German Gains Large but Illusory While Soviet Has Means to Resist

lead_paragraph: The battle for Moscow ended its twentieth day yesterday, with great armies locked in a welter of bloody fighting from the northern reaches of the icy Volga to the warm waters of the Southern Don.
abstract: H W Baldwin on USSR's will to fight
